This paper involves the use of deep reinforcement learning and graphical physics networks to learn intuitive physics models. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the sub-categories of Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Machine Learning (cs.LG), Robotics (cs.RO), Computer Vision (cs.CV), and Systems and Control (cs.SY).
